Usage: addHaloToBlock [-help] <left_bottom_right_top> [-fromInstBox]
                      [-ori <orientation>] [-snapToSite] [<inst_name> | -allMacro  | -allBlackBox  | -allCommitPtn  | -allBlock  | -allIOPad  | -cell <name>]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
<left_bottom_right_top>                  # halo of 4 side: left bottom right
                                         # top (box, required)
<inst_name>                              # for instance (string, optional)
-allBlackBox                             # for all blackBoxs (bool, optional)
-allBlock                                # for all blocks (bool, optional)
-allCommitPtn                            # for all partitions (bool, optional)
-allIOPad                                # for all Io Pads (bool, optional)
-allMacro                                # for all Macros (bool, optional)
-cell <name>                             # by cell name (string, optional)
-fromInstBox                             # for all blocks (bool, optional)
-ori <orientation>                       # base on orientation
                                         # (string, optional)
-snapToSite                              # halo box will snap to site
                                         # (bool, optional)